'''馬可·卡斯泰利'''（{{lang-it|Marco Castelli}}，{{Bd|1990年|6月7日}}<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Models：Marco Castelli|url=https://models.com/models/marco-castelli|accessdate=2021-01-27|author=|date=|format=|publisher=models.com|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127081749/https://models.com/models/marco-castelli|archivedate=2021-01-27}}</ref>），是[[意大利|意大利]]男模<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Marco Castelli, da Porto Empedocle a Milano, Parigi, New York|url=https://www.lasicilia.it/news/agrigento/218779/marco-castelli-da-porto-empedocle-a-milano-parigi-new-york.html|accessdate=2021-01-27|author=Rita Baio|date=2019-01-29|format=|publisher=www.lasicilia.it|language=it|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127080835/https://www.lasicilia.it/news/agrigento/218779/marco-castelli-da-porto-empedocle-a-milano-parigi-new-york.html|archivedate=2021-01-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>、服装设计师<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=Moda: giovane stilista siciliano veste famiglia reale Qatar|url=https://www.ansa.it/sicilia/notizie/2019/04/01/moda-giovane-stilista-siciliano-veste-famiglia-reale-qatar_222f827b-6186-454f-9af1-298dcb89a6a1.html|accessdate=2021-01-27|author=Redazione ANSA|date=2019-04-01|format=|publisher=www.ansa.it|language=it|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420224151/https://www.ansa.it/sicilia/notizie/2019/04/01/moda-giovane-stilista-siciliano-veste-famiglia-reale-qatar_222f827b-6186-454f-9af1-298dcb89a6a1.html|archivedate=2021-04-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>，曾为[[香奈儿|香奈儿]]拍摄广告<ref name=":0" />。

== 生平 ==
馬可·卡斯泰利出生于[[圣卡塔尔多|圣卡塔尔多]]，后与家人在[[阿格里真托省|阿格里真托省]]的[[恩佩多克莱港|恩佩多克莱港]]生活了近20年，并曾在14岁时当过焊工。2010年，他毕业于当第一所名为Nicolò Gallo的学校商业和旅游服务专业。

=== 职业生涯 ===
馬可·卡斯泰利在高中毕业后曾在[[西西里岛|西西里岛]]做救生员<ref name=":1" />，后与米兰一家模特经纪公司签约<ref name=":0" />，从此他搬到了[[米蘭|米兰]]<ref name=":1" />。2011年，他与意大利设计师{{Internal link helper/en|Gianfranco Ferré|Gianfranco Ferré}}签订了第一份合同<ref name=":1" />，开始其模特生涯。

馬可·卡斯泰利在25岁时开始从事时装设计工作，并于2016年推出Marco Castelli Collection自主服饰系列<ref>{{Cite web|title=Exclusive Video Premiere: Marco Castelli – “Il RICHIAMO DELLA MUSA”|url=http://topmeganews.com/exclusive-video-premiere-marco-castelli/|accessdate=2021-01-27|author=|date=2017-03-17|format=|publisher=http://topmeganews.com/|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420061233/http://topmeganews.com/exclusive-video-premiere-marco-castelli/|archivedate=2021-04-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年，他出席了[[戛纳电影节|戛纳电影节]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Alessandro Nava e Marco Castelli al Festival di Cannes 2018|url=https://starssystem.it/think-tank/cannes-2018-follia-diventa-sogno/attachment/cannes_1-1/|accessdate=2021-01-27|author=|date=|format=|publisher=starssystem.it|language=it|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127085137/https://starssystem.it/think-tank/cannes-2018-follia-diventa-sogno/attachment/cannes_1-1/|archivedate=2021-01-27}}</ref>；还作为男模为香奈儿的BLEU DE CHANEL Parfum香水拍摄了广告<ref>{{Cite web|title=Marco Castelli: «Come l’acacia, che si piega ma non si spezza, anche noi torneremo a rinascere dopo la pandemia»|url=https://www.wondernetmag.com/2020/06/16/marco-castelli-come-lacacia-che-si-piega-ma-non-si-spezza-anche-noi-torneremo-a-rinascere-dopo-la-pandemia/|accessdate=2021-01-27|author=Anna Chiara Delle Donne|date=2020-06-16|format=|publisher=www.wondernetmag.com|language=it|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127092109/https://www.wondernetmag.com/2020/06/16/marco-castelli-come-lacacia-che-si-piega-ma-non-si-spezza-anche-noi-torneremo-a-rinascere-dopo-la-pandemia/|archivedate=2021-01-27}}</ref>。

2019年，担任[[卡塔尔|卡塔尔]]王室的服装设计师<ref name=":2" />。

